Package org.ardverk.collection

Interface Summary
Cursor<K,V> A Cursor can be used to traverse a Trie, visit each node step by step and make Cursor.Decisions on each step how to continue with traversing the Trie.
Key<K> An interface that PatriciaTrie keys may implement.
KeyAnalyzer<K> The KeyAnalyzer provides bit-level access to keys for the PatriciaTrie.
Trie<K,V> Defines the interface for a prefix tree, an ordered tree data structure.
 

Class Summary
AbstractKeyAnalyzer<K> An abstract implementation of KeyAnalyzer.
ByteArrayKeyAnalyzer A KeyAnalyzer for byte[]s
ByteKeyAnalyzer A KeyAnalyzer for Bytes
CharacterKeyAnalyzer A KeyAnalyzer for Characters.
CharArrayKeyAnalyzer An KeyAnalyzer for char[]s
DefaultKeyAnalyzer<K extends Key<K>> An implementation of KeyAnalyzer that assumes all keys have the Key interface implemented.
IntegerKeyAnalyzer A KeyAnalyzer for Integers.
LongKeyAnalyzer A KeyAnalyzer for Longs
PatriciaTrie<K,V> PATRICIA Trie
ShortKeyAnalyzer A KeyAnalyzer for Shorts
StringKeyAnalyzer A KeyAnalyzer for Strings.
Tries A collection of Trie utilities
 

Enum Summary
Cursor.Decision The Cursor.Decision tells the Cursor what to do on each step while traversing the Trie.
